  \section mainpage_what Abstract

  This is an open source library for Hokuyo URG laser range scanners.  This library has been tested for the following environments.

- Visual C++ 2005
- Visual C++ 2010
- gcc 4.6.0 (Linux)
- gcc 4.6.2 (MinGW)

